      <title>[제23회 부천판타스틱영화제] 개막식 간단 후기</title>
      <author>doona09</author>
      <publisher>네이버 블로그</publisher>
      <date>2019-06-28 07:18:41</date>
      <dateCrawl>2019-08-07 02:48:24</dateCrawl>
      <url>http://blog.naver.com/PostView.nhn?blogId=doona90&logNo=221572597343</url>
